Rating: 3
Could this get any easier??? I was initially daunted by this recipe after reading previous reviews and the problems they had with rolling out the pastry. Throw the pastry in the freezer for 15min and roll out between waxed paper (lightly floured).... it worked like a charm. Very flaky and flavourful.

