Rating: 4
This really is the best pie crust recipe I've ever made! Using more butter than shortening is the key. When I bake pies at Thanksgiving, everyone insists on having seconds and thirds! Also, you don't need to use a food processor. Use a pastry cutter and fork and process by hand. It works!